title: Neff Charity Dodgeball | King Bach & Celebs
description:
No wrenches were thrown in the Neff sponsored charity dodgeball tournament but we still had a good time! King Bach brought along his celebrity friends for the first in a series of charity sports events.

Teams played for the right to face King Bach's celebrity dodgeball team in the final match of the day and take home the $500 prize.

All of the proceeds from the event went towards the RuJohn Foundation
